OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome good
OL,6,Fspells of evening sunshine, and long
OL,7,Fclear spells overnight, with just a
OL,8,Ffew showers around. Touch of frost
OL,9,Fpossible in sheltered spots. Winds
OL,10,Feasing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FSunny spells and with a few
OL,13,Fshowers around through the morning,
OL,14,Fbut the afternoon looks largely dry
OL,15,Fwith more in the way of sunshine.
OL,16,FNorthwesterly breeze continuing to
OL,17,Fease.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
