OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fmorning with sunny spells Saturday but
OL,7,Fcloud increasing with rain spreading
OL,8,Feast in afternoon. Sunny spells and
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy showers Sunday then
OL,10,Fmostly cloudy with rain at times
OL,11,FMonday.
